1.click start game
2.creat user's block and food's block
3.user move (the velocity is constant -- temporary)
	if click up --movetop
	elsif click down --movebot
	elsif click left --moveleft
	elsif click right --moveright
4.when user move
	if eat food
		speedup
		creat new food
		the point increase
		the body larger
	if the body at same position
		show the gameover screen
		show the score
		all the action stop
5.click game
6.clikc start game
